        "created_at": "2021-04-30T09:07:07.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>For my 50th birthday a couple years ago, I had a gathering where we opened several vintages of Haut Brion, including the 89, 78, 58, 53 and 28.  For the majority the clear winner was the 53, which most picked for the WOTN (among about 15 wines in total).  It is spectacular.</p>",
